## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="ee838-157">複数値の文字列プロパティの値を使用する場合、<xref:System.DirectoryServices.PropertyValueCollection.Remove%2A>メソッドは、正しいアイテムが正常に削除します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee838-157">When working with a multi-valued string property value, the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.PropertyValueCollection.Remove%2A> method will successfully remove the correct item.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee838-158">ただし、名前で、正しいアイテムを識別するは複数値 DNWithString プロパティの値が困難 (DNWithString 項目の格納に使用される、DNWithString COM クラスには、項目を表す 2 つの文字列プロパティがあります)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee838-158">However, identifying the correct items by name is difficult with a multi-valued DNWithString property value (as the DNWithString COM class, which is used to store the DNWithString items, has 2 string properties representing the item).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee838-159">このような項目を削除する方法は、(ループしてすべての項目から)、コレクション内のオブジェクトを呼び出してを検索する、<xref:System.DirectoryServices.PropertyValueCollection.Remove%2A>関数を検出したオブジェクトのポインター。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee838-159">The way to remove such items is to find the object in the collection (by looping thru all the items), then call the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.PropertyValueCollection.Remove%2A> function with the object's pointer that you just found.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ee838-160">これは、次の例に示します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee838-160">This is illustrated in the example below.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```csharp  
  
// Bind to the AD object  
DirectoryEntry myUser = new DirectoryEntry("LDAP://AdServer:389/CN=MyUsername,CN=Users,DC=contoso,DC=com");  
  
// Get the attribute  
PropertyValueCollection testAttribute = myUser.Properties["someAttribute"];  
  
// Find the item in the collection that we want to delete  
DNWithString dnwsItemToRemove = null;  
foreach (DNWithString dnwsItem in testAttribute)  
{  
    if (dnwsItem.StringValue.Equals("SomeValue"))  
    {  
        dnwsItemToRemove = dnwsItem;  
        break;  
    }  
}  
  
// Delete it  
testAttribute.Remove(dnwsItemToRemove);  
  
// Store the data  
myUser.CommitChanges();  
```
